column2: (U)         Fully Unified - Used to identify entities that are measured and reported completely based on Panel-Centric Unified (Panel + Census) measurement.
(u)         Partially Unified - Used to identify entities with at least one child entity that is Fully Unified, but not all.
C         Census Only - Used to identify entities that are measured and reported completely based on Census without panel.
++         Used to identify entities that are projected completely based on the entity?s census tagged data.
+         Used to identify entities with at least one child entity that is projected completely based on the child?s census tagged data , but not all.
w/History         Trend combines media previously reported under different parent and/or different level.
*         Indicates that the entity has assigned traffic to certain pages in the domain to other entities
**         Indicates that the entity is an advertising network.
(v)         Indicates that the advertising network has been verified by comScore.
...         Indicates data used fell below minimum reporting standards and/or data not available.
N/A         Indicates data is not available in the data set for reporting for the specified time period.
#         Caution - small base may result in unstable projection.
##         Directional purposes only - base too unstable for reliable projection.
comScore made an update to Worldwide population estimate. Please refer to http://mymetrix.comscore.com/app/ExtendedMMXUniversalFootNote.aspx for more information.

UV(000) measure for [P] Prisa in December 2012 was understated in Spanish and WW data sets due to a processing issue. The revised UV(000) for [P] Prisa is 11,624 for Spain and 27,175 for WW. For communication purposes, please refer to the [P] Prisa revised
La cifra de Visitantes únicos mes de Diciembre 2012 para [P] Prisa debe ser corregida por una incidencia en el proceso de datos, siendo los datos correctos los siguientes [P] Prisa 11.624 (UV) para España y  27.175(UV) para el dato mundial. Para cualquier comunicación se debe utilizar el dato de [P] Prisa corregido.
Due to the inadvertent exclusion of valid traffic, [P] BABYLON.COM data for August 2012 was understated. The revised measures are as follows: UV (000) 115,477; PV (MM) 1,853.
Due to the inadvertent exclusion of valid traffic, [P] BABYLON.COM data for September 2012 was understated. The revised measures are as follows: UV (000) 115,705; PV (MM) 1,819.
For Jan 2012 to Mar 2012, comScore updated its dictionary definition for [P] FACEBOOK.COM. This resulted in an inorganic decline in page views and duration in the data.

In March 2012, [P] Prisa was inadvertently included in the News/Information category. As a result, [M] El Pais Sites does not appear in the News/Information category rankings independently and is currently located within the expanded (P) Prisa property.  This will be rectified with April 2012 data, when [M] El Pais Sites will appear in the rankings for the category News/Information in its own right and [P] Prisa property will be re-classified under Corporate Presence.  For communication purposes, please refer to the [M] El Pais Sites March 2012 data that is located in the News/Information category within the expanded [P] Prisa property.  
En Marzo 2012, [P] Prisa fue incluida de forma inadvertida en la categoría de News/Information. Por esta razón [M] El Pais Sites no aparece en la categoría News/Information de forma independiente , encontrándose debajo de la property [P] Prisa, siendo subsanado en los datos de Abril 2012, en los cuales [M] El Pais Sites aparecerá en los rankings de la categoría News/Information y [P] Prisa en la categoría de Corporate Presence. Para cualquier comunicación se debe utilizar el dato de El País Sites, que en los datos de Marzo aparece debajo de la property  [P] Prisa en la categoría de News/Information.

In March 2012, [M] Agoda (part of [P] Priceline.com Incorporated) was under-reported as several Agoda-owned domains were inadvertently omitted from the [M] Agoda dictionary definition and were reported under the newly created property AGODA COMPANY. All Agoda-owned domains will be re-included [M] Agoda (part of [P] Priceline.com Incorporated) with April-12 reporting. The March 2012 data for [P] Priceline.com Incorporated with all Agoda-owned domains are for WW: UV (000) 55,773; PV (MM) 747; Min (MM) 591 and US: UV (000) 14,275; PV (MM) 209; Min (MM) 132; and for [M] Agoda for WW: UV (000) 9,236; PV (MM) 99; Min (MM) 70 and for US: UV (000) 425; PV (MM) 3; Min (MM) 3.
